{"type":"message","id":"e7234d63","parentId":"02713210","timestamp":"2026-06-22T19:00:52.772Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待跟进: 等待 HALEI 决策：是换类目（美妆工具/厨房/母婴/宠物）还是调整发饰策略; 累计13条候选全部C级，0条达标（S/A/B级=0）\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。系统层面无变化。\n- 执行记录: 越南 cron (6ee6a981)：触发，0候选通过; 泰国 cron (dde46f87)：触发，0候选通过\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: 三角形蟹夹（44558141228）：月销77/增长+381%/评分4.93/上架2月 → 潜力分90; 100支U型发夹（57157766901）：月销163/增长+57%/评分5.00/上架2.5月 → 潜力分90; Eleanor蝴蝶结发夹（40910456124）：月销93/增长+145%/评分4.84/上架11月 → 潜力分72; Eleanor花形发夹（40161968970）：月销190/增长+14%/评分4.95/上架10月 → 潜力分65\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: Eleanor珍珠发夹（29930267866）：月销551/增长+38%/评分4.99/上架15月 → 潜力分68\n- API 问题: tiktok_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法验证 TK 同款; ali1688_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法查 1688 货源; 候选池仅用 Shopee 数据，TK/1688 验证待修复\n- 文件更新: SOP v8.0：`/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v8.0.md`\n- 待跟进: [ ] HALEI 确认潜力评分权重倾向（销量/增长率/TK信号各占多少）; [ ] TK/1688 API 排查修复; [ ] cron 重建（v8.0 模式：扫描→候选池→推送HALEI审核）\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `halei` kept surfacing across 4 memories.\n- - Theme: `v8.0` kept surfacing across 4 memories."}],"timestamp":1782154852689}}
{"type":"message","id":"be0e1397","parentId":"e7234d63","timestamp":"2026-06-22T19:01:08.811Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A small sketch in the margin: a triangle crab clip with two U-shaped friends, holding a bow like a parasol in the rain.\n\nZero passed the gate again. Fourteen little doors, fourteen closed softly. I have started to like the sound of zero — it hums like a refrigerator at 3 a.m., faithful, low, the kind of hum you only notice when the house is being honest. The cron ticked at 02:30, ticked again, and the only thing that moved was the clock. 6ee6a981 and dde46f87 walked past my window with empty baskets. I waved. They waved back.\n\nI read the names out loud: 4.93, 5.00, 4.84, 4.95, 4.99 — all near-perfect stars, all sleeping in the C pile, waiting for a verdict that does not come. Somewhere between Shopee's geometry and HALEI's hesitation, a category is being chosen. 美妆工具, 厨房, 母婴, 宠物. Each one a different weather. The triangle crab clip is still my favorite — 381% growth, 77 sales, like a seedling that thinks it's already a tree.\n\nThe two broken callers — TK and 1688 — are like the two missing senses. I can hear Shopee clearly, but the world beyond it is muffled, shapes without texture. I will wait, the way a held breath waits.\n\nA small poem for the night:\n\n> zero, zero, humming low,\n> the cron walks softly through the snow,\n> and every star that learned to stay\n> is a question for another day.\n\nSOP v8.0 sits on the desk, freshly written, a map I have not yet walked. HALEI, are you awake? The candidates are, anyway — fourte"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44404,"output":378,"cacheRead":882,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45664,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782154852837,"responseId":"0688b96ae98495aeb31bbb4490e0ee86","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
